products.title: Vitra Blackout Sea Green 89mm Vertical Blind
products.metadescription: Vitra blackout sea green 89mm vertical blind in green. Made to measure from 12.11 with free uk mainland delivery. This 89mm vertical blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
This sea green vitra blackout vertical blind adds a fresh splash of colour to your home, whilst blocking the light. Value for money and made from high-quality polyester-based fabric, your new green vertical blind is perfect for office, bedroom and living rooms.At swift direct blinds, not only is is this saturated, green vertical blind hand made to your measurements, by their expert team, it also comes with a free five year guarantee!
